data.description: Great 3 Bedroom 2 Bath home available! Split Bedroom floor plan. This home features a formal dining room as well as an eat-in kitchen. You'll fall in love with the layout. On the second floor there is an unfinished attic space that can easily turn into another bedroom or Gameroom. The backyard is fully fenced and has a covered patio as well as a storage shed for all your lawn equipment. This property is the perfect canvas for a first-time homeowner. Begin your homeownership journey with a solid foundation and relish the freedom to personalize further, making it uniquely yours. Don't miss out on this gem in Olive Branch. Your next chapter starts here.
